data.description: Perfect opportunity to own a wonderful starter home on the NW side of Tucson,  This home features 2 bedrooms and 1 bath with an open concept living area that connects into the kitchen to provide a larger feel.  Conveniently located to near dining, shopping, and other amenities.  Easy access to I-10.  the home has been well cared for and a brand new HVAC system was just installed in 2023.  Come see this home today!
